title: Natural Soap Making by Elizabeth Letcavage
description:
Natural Soap Making by Elizabeth Letcavage

Overview: How to make cold-process soap (soap from scratch) using only natural fragrances, colorants, and texture additives

Information on different kinds of oils and botanical additives and the special properties they give to the soap

How to make soap with layers, swirls, soap nuggets, and confetti
Includes 12 special soap recipes--oatmeal, milk, and honey soap; gardener's hand soap; all-natural shampoo bar; and more--along with tips for creating your own natural recipes
